CLAUDE.md

# integration test build output
.integration-build

# Android native port — build output only.
# The port's source lives on the android branch, which carries its own
# android/.gitignore (and one per module). These rules exist so the artifacts
# left behind after building there don't show up as untracked noise on main,
# or get swept into a `git add -A`. Deliberately scoped to generated paths, so
# that if the port is merged here its source is still tracked normally.
android/**/.gradle/
android/**/build/
android/**/.cxx/
android/captures/
android/local.properties
# Room's exported schema JSON. Mirrors the decision already made in
# android/data-layer/room/.gitignore on the port's branch — the SQL contract is
# verified by the schema-verify module instead. (Android projects more often
# commit these, since Room uses them to validate migrations; changing that is a
# call for the port, not something to override from here.)
android/**/schemas/
